overview: Gina who is about to get married, when her friends “kidnap” her for a last all-out bachelorette party. Dressed in red latex and all on her own in the Norwegian woods, Gina has to complete a creepy game of challenges. But what starts off as fun soon turns seriously weird, when disturbing events start occurring. Is it part of the planning – or is Gina about to lose her grip of reality?
title: All Must Die
